Package: strategery
Type: Package
Title: Quant Strategy Specification, Backtesting, Optimization And Statistical
    Analysis Workflow
Version: 0.2
Date: 2014-05-26
Author: Daniel Krizian <daniel.krizian@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Daniel Krizian <daniel.krizian@gmail.com>
Description: System for testing strategies. The goal is to combine simple
    abstraction high-level syntax similar to Amibroker's AFL language
    (www.amibroker.com), flexibility of R - for example, Amibroker/Tradestation
    are constrained to technical analysis and can't work flexibly with
    fundamental data (quant value screen historical backtests) speed of
    data.table - which is implemented in C++, has faster sorting algos vs xts
    and uses database concepts.
License: TBD
